# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc
plan.txt
tfplan

# Provider lock files ARE committed (pin versions) — do not ignore .terraform.lock.hcl

# terraform.tfvars here holds only non-sensitive config (region, names, domain) and IS
# committed so the config is the single source of truth. Keep auto-loaded and any
# secret-bearing tfvars out of git.
*.auto.tfvars
*.auto.tfvars.json
secret*.tfvars
*-secrets.tfvars

# Secrets / local env
.env
*.pem
*.key
